    "required_age": "18",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/dc15e30cba407868258f0dad9254a1b9.poster.avif?t=1771586010\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/dc15e30cba407868258f0dad9254a1b9.webm?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/dc15e30cba407868258f0dad9254a1b9.mp4?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>一</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名客人已经死亡……而且，人人均有嫌疑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《欺杀旅社》的神圣大厅。与其他少数人一样，你被选中参与一场交织着死亡、欺诈和推理的一夜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会成为一匹恶狼、潜伏于阴影之中进行狩猎吗？又抑或是，一只拥有相应的技能和手段来予以反击的羔羊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要相信任何人，质疑所见的一切。杀人凶手就隐匿在众目睽睽之下——甚至有可能就是你最亲密的“盟友”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有瞒天过海，方能存活下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高速悬疑解密，凭实力定输赢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶狼，会是谁呢……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总计 24 名玩家，将会参与到一场仅限一夜的凶杀悬疑游戏之中。其中一些会扮演恶狼、其余的所有玩家都将化身羔羊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶狼需要伪装自己、混入羔羊之中，隐藏自己的本性、耐心等待适合的时机出手。不过，亲爱的羔羊、请不要害怕，你们在数量上占据上风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事态想必会混乱至极，你会对自己身边的所有人抱持怀疑、也会被卷入紧张万分的血战之中。虽然性命堪忧，不过我们可以保证——最后的这一段时光，将会令你永生难忘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搜集证据，揭开真相</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一处犯罪现场都会留下相关的线索——头发、指纹、血液、布片……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >证据究竟指向何人？搜集到的证据越多，就越容易锁定罪魁祸首。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/f78d477d0fc6fc27c317b70f364bb076.poster.avif?t=1771586010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/f78d477d0fc6fc27c317b70f364bb076.webm?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >规则</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获胜方法非常简单、明了——只要将对方队伍消灭殆尽即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场围绕恶狼与羔羊展开的殊死之战。谁会主宰这场游戏呢？是在数量上占据上风的羔羊、还是潜伏在羊群之中的恶狼？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过对于羔羊来说，还有其他更为明智的取胜途径——逃之夭夭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否逃离这座城堡呢？只要集齐钥匙、解锁通往港口的大门，然后升起船锚即可。易如反掌，对吧？不过，你真的能相信与自己并肩作战的这些人吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/b46997cc4ba697449afb08da7ca55245.avif?t=1771586010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras_big/b46997cc4ba697449afb08da7ca55245.avif?t=1771586010 width=800 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实力至上——绝不留情！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有投票或是质疑的环节。一旦找到杀人凶手，就准备进行战斗吧。只要够强大、或是够聪明，就能活下来。如若力有未逮，倒下的便将是你自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/8e90ba9ef54477ce6ee6e85c787475a3.poster.avif?t=1771586010\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/8e90ba9ef54477ce6ee6e85c787475a3.webm?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想杀谁，就杀谁</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各式各样的物品隐藏在城堡里的各个角落：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-能让你奋力一搏的枪械和近战武器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-陷阱和专门为夺取性命而调配的毒药</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-能保护自己的护甲和防毒面具</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并不存在必胜法。想要取得最终的胜利，就得玩出自己的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/7b686fada62622a7002b4b348a1471f2.avif?t=1771586010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras_big/7b686fada62622a7002b4b348a1471f2.avif?t=1771586010 width=800 height=189 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聚集模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升感知能力，不错过任何细节。通过聚焦模式，将能看到杀人凶手的足迹、留下的弹壳和砸碎的玻璃，甚至可以透过墙壁听见声响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/079bb5a60c851aea27b10af98e4f8bbe.poster.avif?t=1771586010\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/079bb5a60c851aea27b10af98e4f8bbe.webm?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1598230/extras/079bb5a60c851aea27b10af98e4f8bbe.mp4?t=1771586010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >令人沉浸其中的 3D 语音聊天</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要私下与他人交谈？只要走近其中一个房间、然后把门给关上即可。《欺杀旅社》所采用的 3D 语音聊天技术能根据玩家所处的位置、彼此之间的距离和周遭的环境对声音效果进行相应的调整。不喜欢语音聊天？无妨，通过各式各样的表情和印花来进行沟通也一样可以。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独一无二的角色，无穷无尽的策略</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你想要成为谁呢？随心所欲地切换身份、扮演各种不同的自我吧。每个角色都身怀不同的绝技——潜行高手、破案专家，甚至还有盗窃大师……利用他们的技能来塑造战术、力挽狂潮吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人攻坚、二人组队、三人成行，甚至是小队行动——都没问题！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是独自攻略、还是组团闯关，这场终极游戏都已为你备好挑战。组成技艺娴熟的破案团体、或是阴险狡诈的猎杀小队，全都由你决定。即使相隔一段距离，队伍成员之间也可以通过语音聊天保持同步、彼此配合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*本游戏仅限在线游玩。如果将来停止运营，将无法再继续游玩。</p>",
